# Game mechanism design
## Construction system
Construction system is the most basic and important system in MyUniversity, it is a grid building system[^1] which allows players to build buildings on a grid plain.

# Reference
[^1]:[Grid building system tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l0emsAHIBjU&list=PLcRSafycjWFepsLiAHxxi8D_5GGvu6arf&ab_channel=SunnyValleyStudio)
